The Rundeck job named "Call a remote 2" is designed to send an HTTP GET request to a specified URL. It requires a single input option, `url`, which must be provided when executing the job. The command utilizes the `HttpWorkflowStepPlugin`, configured to disable response code checking and to not print the response or response code. The request is sent to the URL specified by the user, with SSL verification enabled and a timeout set to 30 seconds.